speaker: Fishcaya
text: You’re still alive? Ugh. Alam mo, nakakainis ka na.

speaker: Dina
text: I’m done running. I’m done denying what I did. Unlike you… I can change. And I will stop you — for my island, for the people, for the future.

speaker: Fishcaya
text: You think the truth will save you?

speaker: Dina
text: No… but it will defeat you.
